data.description: Step into a realm of unparalleled elegance at 7111 Starmount Court, a masterfully crafted residence by NVHomes West in 2022. This property, virtually untouched and still radiating the freshness of new construction, beckons you with its opulent offerings. Upon entering the main foyer, an office and sitting room grace your right—a harmonious blend of productivity and tranquility—while a thoughtfully placed half bath adorns the left, seamlessly integrating convenience into the main floor.  The journey through the main hall unveils an expansive open concept living room, kitchen, and dining room. A chef's haven, the kitchen captivates with a colossal island, an abundance of cabinet space, gleaming stainless steel appliances, luxurious marble countertops, and an artistic tile backsplash. The culinary experience is elevated with a pantry and a mudroom, enhancing the practicality of this sophisticated abode.  Ascend to the upper level, where four bedrooms, each adorned with its own attached bathroom, await. The primary suite, a testament to luxury, boasts two walk-in closets and an attached bath featuring dual vanities, a deep soaking tub, and a lavish stall shower with indulgent bench seating.  Yet, the allure of this residence extends beyond the ordinary. The lower level beckons with a recreation room, offering an expansive canvas for entertaining. A full bath and a meticulously designed wet bar add to the lower level's allure. Notable features include a cutting-edge reverse osmosis water filtration system, an active radon system, a whole house humidifier, a rejuvenating sauna in the basement, an electric car charger discreetly nestled in the garage, and a saltwater jacuzzi hot tub gracing the patio, inviting you to unwind in style. The whole house is also pre-wired for outside cameras.   Parking becomes a seamless affair with the attached 3-car garage and an expansive driveway. Nestled in the highly sought-after Lake Linganore Association, this property opens the door to a myriad of amenities—two private beaches, tennis courts, four swimming pools, and meandering hiking trails. The community's vibrant spirit is reflected in its diverse events, from festive holiday celebrations to the charm of farmers markets and the allure of food trucks.   But that's not all; this residence also opens the door to some of the best public schools in Maryland, including Blue Heron Elementary, Oakdale Middle, and Oakdale High. Your pursuit of excellence extends beyond the home into the realm of education.  This isn't just a home; it's an immersive experience, where every detail is a brushstroke on the canvas of comfort, convenience, and lavish living. Embrace the opportunity to claim this piece of paradise in Lake Linganore as your own, where the essence of luxury is woven into every fiber of its being.
